YOUETIXCOMUNIDAD: YouEtix is an ethical community, a circuit of businesses, shopkeepers and professionals that choose to use a part of their income to pay the word of mouth of ethical citizens.
INCIUDADANOETICO: An Ethical citizen is a person who joins the Etix community and receives a reward when suggesting the affiliated shops.
COMOCONVERTIRSE: How to become an Ethical citizen
DESCARGANDOLAAPLICACION: By downloading the EtixPay app, respecting and agreeing to the ethical charter, by generating Reward Points and helping the community to grow.
SONLAMONEDADELBOCAABOCA: They are the 'currency' of the word of mouth, the value that the ethical shops assign to good tips. Ethical citizens are given Reward Points for every purchase in the affiliated businesses. Every month, the Reward Points of reached level of earnings are converted into real money and paid to each ethical citizen.
CUALESSONLOSNIVELES: What are the levels of earnings
ENETIXHAY10NIVELES: In Etix, there are 11 levels of earnings, the more Reward Points your community generates, the higher level you reach. You earn by difference taking into consideration the level of friends in your community.
SITUCOMUNIDAD: If your community reaches a higher level, it is also thanks to all the communities created by your friends. In a concept of meritocratic economy and ethical community, everyone must be rewarded for their work. You get your earnings after recognizing the earnings to your community friends, corresponding to the level they reached.
HACIENDOLOQUESIEMPREHASHECHO: By doing what you have always done, by suggesting businesses, shops and professionals of the circuit which you had a positive experience with. Send your community code to your friends or acquaintances, when they become ethical citizens through your code, they automatically make part of your community and help increase your reward level.
COMOSELLAMAESTAFORMADEINGRESO: What is this form of earning called
ESTAESTRUCTURA: This structure is called the circular economy because all the members of the community help each other and they generate shared wealth.
PODRASEMPEZAR: You can start spending your money in affiliated shops, you can suggest your favorite shops and pay with traditional currencies or with TIXs.
LOSTIXSON: TIXs are credits that can be accumulated on your Etix account. 1 TIX is worth 1 Euro and it is accepted within the Etix circuit. TIXs can be spent without commissions and redeemed for real money at any time.
ETIXPARTICIPA: How Etix helps in the neighborhoods
UNAPARTEDELDINEO: A part of money spent by ethical citizens is used for neighborhood charity support. If you shop in a local supermarket, you may be helping a family in your area to pay their electricity bill.
CONQUIENCOMPARTIMOS: With whom we share the personal data of ethical citizens
SIMPLENOLOSCOMPARTIMOS: We don't share them with anyone, personal data remain within the community.
UTILIZAESTECHATENVIVO: If you need help when introducing the Etix community to a new Ethical citizen, use this live chat support.
